import React from 'react'
import './style.scss'

export default () => {
  return (
    <form
      method='post'
      className='upload-form'
      >
      <input type='file'/>
      <input
        type='submit'
        value='ADD file'
        accept='.text, .json'
      />
    </form>
  )
}
